A disturbing scene emerged on Tuesday in Abuja, the Federal Capital Territory, where some youths around Apo Bridge roundabout mobbed a trailer load of rice and illegally deposed it of some of the commodity. READ ALSO:  Covid-19: Daura gets fully-equipped Isolation Centre The driver of the truck had slowed down trying to navigate a minor hold up, when some boys who had gathered around the area stormed the vehicle and carted away bags of rice. Some of the hoodlums climbed the truck and were throwing down bags of rice from the truck even as it drove off. Some of them said they haen trailing the truck with rice load from a distance.